text.tspan: Matty was never good with money which always
caused him to take up… let's just say not so favorable
jobs to get by. Matty ended up double crossing the MCS,
pocketing the money. But worst of all he gave The Boss
the stink eye, which was the straw that broke the camel’s
back. The boss summoned Mustardman to whisk Matty
away to the stampede room and at that point there was
no going back for Matty. He’s spent the past 10 years tied
to a chair in front of a projector playing ‘add round stampede
videos’ on repeat. A constant loop of CGI zoo animals,
CGI dinosaurs, Cartoonmania characters, BFDI characters,
Buzz on Maggie characters, and Splaat. Matty hasn’t quite
been the same since, having paranoid delusions of various
different characters and animals running across his line
